G04 Copper layer 5 (GND plane with embedded traces) - Atari Falcon rev4 (Sparrow, C303006-001)*
G04 Converted from Seetrax RANGER RS-274-D: SPARL5.SPL (clear) + SPARL5A.SPL (dark)*
G04 Apertures from SPARROW.USR symbol table*
G04 Translated by (-4849,-7746) mil into the Drill_PTH.drl (rev2 KiCad) coordinate frame*
G04 Original artwork is a negative-plane pair; rebuilt here as a*
G04 positive composite: solid flood (dark), then SPARL5.SPL clearances (LPC),*
G04 then SPARL5A.SPL pads (LPD). Pads without an antipad in*
G04 the clear pass connect directly to the plane (no thermal relief),*
G04 matching the original film composite.*
